node.text:
Listed by @3SAEstate 🔑🌴
This villa impresses with its highest quality, cutting-edge technology, and magnificent contemporary design. 🤍

It’s a fabulous eco-friendly house that has been thoughtfully planned and is turned into a very practical and functional home providing the best of the Mediterranean lifestyle. ☀️

📍 Benahavis

Property details:
• Surface 630M²⁠⠀⁠
• Plot 1285M²⠀
• 5 Bedrooms⁠⠀
• ⁠Sea views
• BBQ Area
• 16m Infinity pool
• Decked solarium

Asking price 3,490,000 €
-

node.text:
@KnightFrankMiddleEast exclusive Signature villa comes with an extended built-up area of 10,00 square feet and of the largest plot sizes on the Palm of 15,682 Sqft, it boasts a number of charming modifications, including fully renovated bedrooms and bathrooms, generously extended guest bedroom with panoramic sea views, an extended master bedroom along with a palatial lounge and cinema room area with an office. 🔑
 
The real talking point is the landscaped front and rear gardens, with an extended outdoor plot size creating a large neatly manicured garden with a stunning swimming pool area looking down the frond. A barbecue and sitting area along with an outdoor bar make this the ideal weekend and evening hangout.
 
For more information or to arrange a private viewing please contact @mrpalmjumeirah

node.text:
@OliverThornton with a special offer known as “The Victoria” - an exceptional development opportunity to build a zen contemporary home w/ pool and ADU/pool house in Venice, CA 🧘‍♀️ 🌊 

💰: Just reduced price on this RTI project to $2,395,000 , Exit price / value of finished home is around $5,500,000.

Extremely rare opportunity to build this one-of-a-kind, permit-issued dream home. The ~5400 sq ft 5 BR / 7 BA contemporary zen residence w/ ADU & street-to-alley access is sited on the largest lot in all of Venice. The proposed Tulum inspired finishes perfectly blend warmth, tranquility, & the Venice beachy & artsy vibes w/ natural materials & textures such as European White Oak, natural stones & tropical landscaping. Waste no time with Coastal Commission or Building & Safety, as this property comes with RTI / ISSUED PERMITS. Existing ~3500 sq ft structure on the property allows for financing with more favorable terms than ground-up construction. Walk or bike to Erewhon, Whole Foods, the ocean, Abbot Kinney, Main St, and all of the restaurants, entertainment and nightlife Venice has to offer. Truly a once in a lifetime opportunity to build an impressive home all while having healthy equity margins from a developer perspective. 

📱: 310-704-1794
💻: Oliver@hollywoodestates.com
